OL,3,C'Wrong bones removed': NHS Trust
OL,4,Capologises after botched surgeries
OL,6,FAn NHS Trust has apologised to the
OL,7,Fpatients of a surgeon who botched
OL,8,Foperations so badly that some had the
OL,9,Fwrong bones removed and were left in
OL,10,Fagonising pain for years.
OL,12,FMian Munawar Shah was suspended from
OL,13,FWalsall Healthcare NHS Trust in 2021 -
OL,14,Ftwo years after the first complaint
OL,15,Fwas made.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, a report detailed a trail
OL,18,Fof disastrous surgeries, with 91
OL,19,Fpatients suffering moderate or severe
OL,20,Fharm.
