OL,4,Capologises after botched surgeries
OL,6,FWhat did the report find?
OL,8,FSome patients were told their pain was
OL,9,Fpsychological when, in reality, he had
OL,10,Ffused the wrong joints together. One
OL,11,Fpatient, expecting a straightforward
OL,12,Fwrist surgery, woke up to find the
OL,13,Fwrong bone had been removed entirely.
OL,15,FAnother had to endure four separate
OL,16,Fsurgeries to try to correct his
OL,17,Fmistakes but was still left in
OL,18,Fpermanent pain.
