OL,6,FOthers who trusted him with their
OL,7,Fshoulder replacements later found out
OL,8,Fthe implants had been placed so badly
OL,9,Fthey dislocated almost immediately,
OL,10,Frequiring emergency corrective
OL,11,Fprocedures.
OL,13,FConcerns were raised again and again
OL,14,Fby physiotherapists, colleagues, and
OL,15,Feven an internal five-year audit that
OL,16,Fflagged a high complication rate in
OL,17,F2020.
