OL,6,FHowever Mr Shah was fully suspended in
OL,7,F2021, after he was found to have
OL,8,Fperformed wrong-site surgery, a
OL,9,Fcatastrophic error known as a 'Never
OL,10,FEvent'.
OL,12,FThe report issued on Tuesday
OL,13,Fcriticises the hospital's failure to
OL,14,Fact, saying its governance systems
OL,15,Fwere too weak to stop him.
OL,17,FJunior staff felt unable to speak up
OL,18,Fand crucial safety checks like proper
OL,19,Fsurgical audits and multidisciplinary
OL,20,Freviews simply didn't happen.
