OL,3,C'Wrong bones removed': NHS Trust
OL,4,Capologises after botched surgeries
OL,6,FIn response, Joanne Chadwick-Bell,
OL,7,FChief Executive for Walsall NHS Trust,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I want to unreservedly
OL,9,Fapologise for the 91 patients who have
OL,10,Fundergone treatment with us, where we
OL,11,Fhaven't given them the outcomes we
OL,12,Fexpect".
OL,14,F"I also want to recognise that those
OL,15,Fpatients who didn't get the care they
OL,16,Fdeserved".
OL,18,F"It would have been distressing them
OL,19,Fto have to relive some of those
OL,20,Fexperiences".
