OL,3,C'Wrong bones removed': NHS Trust
OL,4,Capologises after botched surgeries
OL,6,FWhen asked if there was a danger that
OL,7,Fanother surgeon could operate within
OL,8,Fthe trust again, she said: "We've put
OL,9,Fa number of things in place from a
OL,10,Fgovernance perspective to make sure
OL,11,Fthis doesn't happen again".
OL,13,F"So should any surgeon want to
OL,14,Fundertake new procedures, where
OL,15,Fperhaps they are new to the trust or
OL,16,Fnew to the doctor, they need to go
OL,17,Fthrough a number of additional checks
OL,18,Ffor us to be assured of their level of
OL,19,Fcompetence".
