OL,3,C'Wrong bones removed': NHS Trust
OL,4,Capologises after botched surgeries
OL,6,FWalsall Healthcare NHS Trust also said
OL,7,Fit had reported the incidents to the
OL,8,Fpolice which has said they gave a
OL,9,Freference number. Police indicated to
OL,10,Fthe trust they would only take any
OL,11,Ffurther action if the General Medical
OL,12,FCouncil agreed it was necessary.
OL,14,FSince Mr Shah operated the NHS Trust
OL,15,Fhas introduced new measures which mean
OL,16,Fthat when doctors want to bring in new
OL,17,Fprocedures, they'd have to go through
OL,18,Fa more robust process.
